This is a theme for the [[[war-on-all-fronts-hub|War on All Fronts]]] Canon. An equivalent version for the Sigma-9 base theme can be found **[[[theme:war-on-all-fronts-sigma|HERE]]]**. Note that the Black Highlighter Theme must be imported alongside this theme to use it. To use this theme on an article, paste the following into your page:

> @@[[include theme:black-highlighter-theme]]@@
> @@[[include theme:war-on-all-fronts-bhl]]@@

